creator: Catalyst Tech
descriptionHtml:
IntoDare is a great way to interact, chat and play with like-minded people all around the world. Get to know each other in a fun game of truth or dare and if you like each other, you can continue chatting afterwards!

We are also a very easy-to-use private chat app with end-to-end encryption. Your privacy comes first, so usernames are key to connecting with users on IntoDare. Send temporary messages, photos and videos to your friends that are destroyed and deleted from our servers after a timer set by you.

DISCOVER YOURSELF
• Discover things you never knew about yourself.
• Don't know what to say? Break the ice with a game of truth or dare!
• Different levels of content so you can start things slow.

EARN MONEY
• Lock your photos and videos for money.
• Receive tips from other users on IntoDare.

PRIVATE & SAFE
• Self-destructing messages, images and videos.
• No messages, images or videos are saved on our servers.
• No ads!

We dare you to have fun!
descriptionShort: A private place where you can indulge your desires with like-minded people.

Play dirty truth or dare with hot singles nearby, meet new people worldwide, chat and flirt with local women and girls. This is what this online dating app is all about.

IntoDare is a secure and private dating app for Android that utilizes the fun truth or dare game and allows you to break the ice and get to know each other better while asking different truth and dares questions. Using this free dating app to make friends and meet new people, you also get to browse through the list of nearby singles and chat and flirt in private chat rooms.

So, if you are into such online dating apps to connect with people in your area, chat and flirt with hot singles worldwide or even play the fun Truth or Dare game, you’ve come to the right place. Download IntoDare for free on your Android device and have fun chatting, flirting, playing, meeting and dating like-minded people.

► Play Truth or Dare, make new friends, and meet like-minded people nearby
IntoDare is a secure online dating app for men and women with any preferences and orientations. This free dating app delivers a trusted community of singles and couples to meet new people, date like-minded persons, chat privately with local singles and flirt with hot girls worldwide. It even sets the bar higher by offering the Truth or Dare game to break the ice and discover things you never knew about yourself.

◆ Break the ice with a game of truth or dare: What makes this dating and relationships app stand out in the competition, is the option to flirt with local singles in a fun game of truth or dare and start dating afterward. It offers different levels of truth or dare content, you can decide whether you want to spice things up or keep things slow.

► Your privacy is our #1 priority: This dating app to meet new people and make friends comes with end-to-end encryption to ensure your conversations are safe and private. When it comes to chatting with strangers and flirting with local girls and women, you can send self-destructive messages for yet another level of privacy.

◆ Why don’t you give this free online dating app to meet new people a try?
Whether you are looking for a dating app to chat with strangers and flirt with hot girls, or you are looking for an online dating app to meet new people and date like-minded singles, we’ve got you covered. This dating & relationships app has also got you covered when you want to play dirty truth or dare and make your relationship move to the next step.

► Get paid for doing what you love! Become a verified profile, after which people can pay to play a round of Truth or Dare or have a chat session with you. You decide the price, duration and how far you go. No strings attached. Additionally, you can sell your content directly to users on IntoDare. Give it a shot!

◆ Since the entire features of this online dating app to chat with local singles are available for free, there is no harm in giving it a try and exploring all the features for yourself.

► IntoDare main features at a glance:
• Clean and neat design with a fresh and intuitive interface
• Secure and safe online dating app for singles and couples
• Play dirty truth or dare to break the ice
• Char with strangers privately with an end-to-end encryption
• Discover like-minded people and make friends
• Flirt with local girls and women nearby
• Send self-destructing messages, photos, and videos
• Proud supporter of the LGBTQ+ community 🏳️‍🌈
• Free to use online dating app to meet new people and make friends
• Earn money by doing chat sessions, truth or dare games or by monetizing your photos and videos.

Stay tuned and let us know about any bugs, questions, feature requests, or any other suggestions.

title: Masked: Hook up, Meet, Dating

creator: Masked App
descriptionHtml:
Welcome to Masked, the dating app that makes it easier to date 💜

In a society that profits on our self-doubt, Masked is the online dating app where it pays to be the real, unapologetic you.

We’re a little different from other dating apps. We fight the ambiguity of modern dating with authentic, unfiltered chats. We believe real connection is born from being honest in who you are and what you really want.

DISCOVER, CHAT & PLAY 👌
Masked is the dating app that allows you to match and chat with people, make friends, or find a partner. We make it easier to meet people near you:

✔ Don’t be shy: Introduce yourself, complete your profile to raise your popularity and get more exposure.

✔ Have fun with our filters: Find friends and dates by using our special filters.

✔ Meet People Nearby: Meet people who live near you, make new friends and chat for free.

✔ Have fun: Play Truth or Dare game to get to know each other.

✔ Better Together: Invite your friends to Masked and match profiles you are interested in.

✔ Intentions: Being on a dating app doesn’t mean you just want to date. You might want something serious, to find friends, play fun games or have a deep chat. Whatever you're here for, let people know.


Start your dating journey today!


GO ON REAL DATES 👆
Whether you’re looking to start dating, have chats, or make friends, you’re sure to find it on Masked.

✔ Ready to chat and date? Our great features mean you’ll be chatting about all sorts of things (like whether or not you’d survive a zombie apocalypse!) before you even get to your date.

✔ Chat for free with singles and make local friends.

✔ Meet our lovely community looking to make friends, go on dates and fall in love.


SAFE AND SECURE 🔒
Masked is a dating app that ensures safety and respect within our community. We do not tolerate any kind of inappropriate behaviour and have strict usage guidelines, as well as an extensive list of safety features to ensure the best dating experience with us.

Safety Centre 💜
Where you can find in depth guides, useful tools and essential helplines to date with confidence and ease.

Private Detector 🚫
This keeps you safe from unsolicited images. If a graphic image is detected in our dating app, we’ll blur it and warn you of the content.

Rude Message Detector ❌
Any insulting, discriminatory or overly sexual messages will be automatically flagged.

Verified profiles ✅
These little ticks means that their dating profile has been vetted by us—and there isn’t a bot on the other side!

Personalised settings 🔧
Tailor your settings to make sure your profile is the way you want it to be, like deciding when you appear online and who can message you.


Start earning money 💰
Get paid for doing what you love! People can pay to play a round of Truth or Dare or have a chat session with you. You decide the price, duration and how far you go. Give it a shot!


BOOST YOUR PROFILE 🔥
Serious about dating? Activate Masked Plus! You'll be able to access plenty of exciting features that will help you get the most out of our app:

⭐️ Find out who viewed your profile and start chatting with local singles.

⭐️ See who liked your profile. It's time to meet new people and make new friends!

⭐️ Play unlimited games without limits.

⭐️ Set your location to anywhere in the world!

⭐️ Get access to exclusive emoticon packages, so you can impress everybody.

⭐️ You can hide your country and current location.

⭐️ Anonymous browsing: Go incognito and browse profiles privately.


The price varies by country and may change without notice, but you can always see the exact price in the app.

Read our Privacy Policy and Terms of Use:
https://www.maskedapp.com/privacy
https://maskedapp.com/terms

✔ Meet our lovely community looking to make friends, go on dates and fall in love.


SAFE AND SECURE 🔒
Masked is a dating app that ensures safety and respect within our community. We do not tolerate any kind of inappropriate behaviour and have strict usage guidelines, as well as an extensive list of safety features to ensure the best dating experience with us.

Safety Centre 💜
Where you can find in depth guides, useful tools and essential helplines to date with confidence and ease.

Private Detector 🚫
This keeps you safe from unsolicited images. If a graphic image is detected in our dating app, we’ll blur it and warn you of the content.

Rude Message Detector ❌
Any insulting, discriminatory or overly sexual messages will be automatically flagged.

Verified profiles ✅
These little ticks means that their dating profile has been vetted by us—and there isn’t a bot on the other side!

Personalised settings 🔧
Tailor your settings to make sure your profile is the way you want it to be, like deciding when you appear online and who can message you.


Start earning money 💰
Get paid for doing what you love! People can pay to play a round of Truth or Dare or have a chat session with you. You decide the price, duration and how far you go. Give it a shot!


BOOST YOUR PROFILE 🔥
Serious about dating? Activate Masked Plus! You'll be able to access plenty of exciting features that will help you get the most out of our app:

⭐️ Find out who viewed your profile and start chatting with local singles.

⭐️ See who liked your profile. It's time to meet new people and make new friends!

⭐️ Play unlimited games without limits.

⭐️ Set your location to anywhere in the world!

⭐️ Get access to exclusive emoticon packages, so you can impress everybody.

⭐️ You can hide your country and current location.

⭐️ Anonymous browsing: Go incognito and browse profiles privately.


The price varies by country and may change without notice, but you can always see the exact price in the app.

MEET NEW PEOPLE IN AWESOME GAMES

Connect with real, like-minded individuals through engaging chats where you can send anonymous messages, Truth or Dare games, and meaningful conversations. YOUR PERFECT MATCH IS A DOWNLOAD AWAY

DISCOVER MASKED LOVE VIBES

Travelling vibes? Get to know the locals, and join a community of people from around the world. Anonymous dating in London, meeting new friends in Miami, or nights out in Berlin: wherever you go, we’ll be there. Some people call us their “most dependable matchmaker app”. Others call us “the world’s most popular free dating site”. But you can just call us when you want to meet up with people in your area.💑

INCLUSIVITY IS KEY

Whether you’re looking for a place to anonymous chat and date, find friends, a gay dating app, a bisexual dating app, a lesbian dating app, an LGBTQ anonymous dating app; We’ve got everything you’re looking for in our lovely community to meet people or talk to strangers.

STRANGER CHAT APP

SAFETY FIRST
This anonymous app has a robust verification process ensures only genuine users join, providing a safe environment for all members.✅

JOIN THE FUN
So what are you waiting for? Download the best free dating app today! It doesn’t matter if you’re looking to make friends, meet new people, play games for fun or find your perfect match, Masked Love is a place where everyone can find exactly what they’re looking for – and it’s time you joined in.
